{"tid":2021140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁天琦紀錄片《地厚天高》現已登陸 iTunes Store","createTime":"2020-05-17T13:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T00:07:28.000Z","uid":134071,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8d36a0913ff2c462d1f50c2ea29df2f36cd0ca","tid":2021140,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:57:04.000Z","msg":"外國都睇到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lostinthefumes/photos/a.271079260053613/971195316708667/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flostinthefumes%2Fphotos%2Fa.271079260053613%2F971195316708667%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=212e3902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lostinthefumes/photos/a.271079260053613/971195316708667/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n地厚天高 Lost In the Fumes<br />\n4 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【《地厚天高》現已登陸 iTunes Store】<br />\n【&quot;Lost in the Fumes&quot; now available on iTunes Store】<br />\n<br />\n立即看： <a href=\"https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2Z7WB8p&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=3aa595ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p</a><br />\n<br />\n經過多月的努力，<strong>《地厚天高》終於在50個國家上架 iTunes Store</strong>。一直以來，我們聽到不少觀眾的反映，希望能簡易地觀看數位高清版本的《地厚天高》。在家裡沒有DVD機、海外的朋友，機會來了！<br />\n<br />\n按以下鏈結或直接於 iTunes 搜尋「Lost In The Fumes」就可以立即串流觀看《地厚天高》！最後，多謝影意志各合作單位的努力，讓這部紀錄片可以走出香港，讓世界各地的更多朋友得悉香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Lost in the Fumes&quot; is now available internationally on iTunes Store on more than 50 countries! For all of you who don't have a DVD player or cannot get the DVD locally, you can now watch the documentary in the comfort of your own home with the newly released digital version.<br />\n<br />\nWe would also like to thank our distributor Ying E Chi for all the efforts that made this possible. Click in the following link for purchase or rental: <a href=\"https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2Z7WB8p&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=3aa595ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p</a><br />\n<br />\n#地厚天高 #iTunes #LostInTheFumes"},{"pid":"e5434e196e3993812c1cd5541fb2b38b6b8d9aa0","tid":2021140,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"支持+share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e815ae166c851a636dc518cfc0d90f82b310e0","tid":2021140,"uid":308567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"[戰略分析]香城ONLINE 527添馬之戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2015261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2015261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27868b96db9726bf414e347fc6c6bc9f25d13787","tid":2021140,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49d6fc750e2954026af372fefef20cd3d84d87c","tid":2021140,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報用戶免費睇"},{"pid":"7fc1c6542e6463f876e974ce5291dd52ef7b8a97","tid":2021140,"uid":342673,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"太貴 不了🙏🏿"},{"pid":"41099805cfd51a388509362379ccaa7096be2bb2","tid":2021140,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"擁"},{"pid":"219f14ea9a40c884d2b76704fb13d29515356915","tid":2021140,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a49d6fc750e2954026af372fefef20cd3d84d87c","tid":2021140,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報用戶免費睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"cd90fd352cec9330f656529315cb013099d3cbc3","tid":2021140,"uid":127862,